## ğŸ™ I. GitHub Account Creation

### ğŸ’¡ Why is a GitHub account important?

GitHub helps you save, share, and manage your code onlineâ€”great for working alone or with a team.

### âœ… Steps:

1. Go to [github.com](https://github.com/) and click **â€œSign up.â€**
2. Use a professional email address.
